v1.0.0.changelog:
Features
* Windows/OS X/Linux Support (32 & 64 bit)
* no .NET or Python installation needed
* drag & drop encrypted (US/EU/JP/KR/TW) or unencrypted .mibs
* create quests from scratch
* export encrypted (US/EU/JP/KR/TW) or unencrypted .mib
* manage your CQs in the editor's library
* integrated proxy to directly host your CQ library
* easy to use interface with autocompletion features
* displays for specific quest ids which monsters are possible
* applies fix for large monsters in the small table
* applies fix to bypass reward check

Current Limitations:
* no episodic or challenge quests are supported right now
